{
  "id": "10072",
  "key": "GG-69",
  "fields": {
    "summary": "Enhance Progress Tracking for JSON Export Status",
    "description": {
      "type": "doc",
      "version": 1,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Use case:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "As a "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Team Gamma member",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "strong"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", "
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "I want to enhance progress tracking for JSON export status, "
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "so that I can monitor the progress of the Jira data export operation."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "rule"
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Acceptance criteria:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "GIVEN",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "em"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " that the JSON export operation is in progress, "
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "WHEN",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "em"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " the backend fetches issues, workflows, screens, and custom fields from Jira Cloud, "
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "AND",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "em"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " stores or caches the results securely before the final export, "
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "THEN",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "em"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " it must provide real-time progress updates to the front end."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "rule"
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Technical notes:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The backend should implement a mechanism to emit real-time updates using WebSocket or polling to communicate the progress status with the front end. The updates should include detailed information about the current operation being performed (e.g., fetching issues, workflows, screens) and indicate completion of each step. This will allow the front end to display a visual representation of the progress and keep track of the ongoing export operation. Additionally, consider implementing a logging mechanism to capture detailed progress and any potential errors during the export process for future reference and troubleshooting."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
